definitions.definition: A use of the mystical term ‘abracadabra’, supposed to work as part of a healing charm or a magical spell ; any spell or incantation making use of the word.
Mumbo jumbo ; obscure language or technicalities ; jargon .
examples: I don’t know all the theoretical abracadabra about how it works, I’m only its pilot.

main_definition: A use of the mystical term ‘abracadabra’, supposed to work as part of a healing charm or a magical spell ; any spell or incantation making use of the word. [from 16th c.]
secondary_definitions: Mumbo jumbo ; obscure language or technicalities ; jargon . [from 19th c.]
